<example>
  <title>Print a square of digits</title>
  <program>
size = int(input("Enter size of square: "))
           
y = 0
while y < size:
    x = 0
    while x < size:
        print((x+y)%10, end='')
        x += 1
    print()    # print a newline
    y += 1

  </program>
  <description>Print a square of digits of a given size.  A square of size of 5 looks like below.
01234
12345
23456
34567
45678</description>
